      "writtenOn": "2017-12-12T12:46:12Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "This change causes us to use bundled recipes, instead of calling recipes.py directly and having it sync the recipe deps.  We were using the depot_tools from recipe deps, which is just a normal checkout.  The bundled recipes are stripped down a bit, so we don\u0027t get all of depot_tools.  In particular, the update_depot_tools script (which is called by the gclient wrapper script) is missing.  So we have to call gclient.py directly.",
